Name: Project Dark
About the game: Project Dark is a story driven first-person horror action maze game. Trapped in a House that no longer feels like your own, the only way out is to face the darkness and find a way to survive. This is the First Installment of Project Dark. With something Lurking in the Dark. You are not alone. There something in there and they are looking for you. You will Have to Face the Darkness to Survive. The question is - Can you Survive? Features: Fast-paced Horror: No hiding in lockers here. Run for your life and run fast. The enemy can be tricked but not for long. High Quality: AAA-quality graphics and creative designs give players a variety of unique and terrifying to survive. Hazardous Environments: Enemy is not the only danger. The House seems like it is alive and it is full of traps, hazards, and other dangers to watch out for. Unique Enemies: Roaming Enemy that will chase you down. A house that will trap you with in it.
